data.name: Tenyi Spirit - Mapura
data.desc: If you control no Effect Monsters: You can Special Summon this card from your hand. When your opponent activates a card or effect that targets a face-up non-Effect Monster(s) you control (Quick Effect): You can banish this card from your hand or GY; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy that card. You can only use each effect of "Tenyi Spirit - Mapura" once per turn.
